When trying to rank new issues on our scrum planning board we get the following error

JIRA Agile cannot execute the rank operation. This board has recently been configured to use the Rank field. The system must be re-indexed before you can rank issues. Ask your administrator to perform a manual re-index.

After reindexing the error still occurs

When upgrading to JIRA Agile 6.4.0.8 the upgrade fails with the error:

{panel}Caused by: java.sql.SQLSyntaxErrorException: ORA-00933: SQL command not properly ended{panel}

The server then shows the following warning at the top of the page:

{panel}*JIRA Agile is currently unavailable. This might be because an upgrade task has failed to run or has not not yet completed.*

Please contact your system administrator if you continue to see this message.{panel}

This leaves the plugin in a broken state which cannot be upgraded or downgraded and a full system restore is required to recover this.
